{
  "stem": "11797.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Very, very bad.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "No food. you-- you-- we were given a tiny piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a torturous camp, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was a tiny piece of bread at night, to eat it tomorrow morning, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So my father, we were there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My father was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My brother was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Maybe had a tiny piece of-- he made me a little bag.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He made me a little bag, little piece of string.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He said, look-- me-- listen [? that, ?] take the piece of bread and put it in that little piece of-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] --bag, you know, he says.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then, he says, now, you eat that tomorrow morning, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And keep it when you sleep.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Hold it like now, so nobody can cut it from you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because there's people who cut it at night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they'll come by-- over with a knife and cut it, you know, and try to steal it from you.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So sleep with your-- with your hand holding on the string.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I-- and we used to go out at night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They used to assign so much-- so many pieces of bread to give each halfling, which means each-- each prison-- prisoner.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So people used to die at night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So in the morning, you know, if somebody died, you know, we used to bring him out dead, holding him.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "When they counted, you know, we had two or three people dead.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Now we got their bread.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Then, after they wrote down 60 or 80 people, we're in the barracks now.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So instead of 58, no, yeah?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we got the piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we would divide it more.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we reported they were dead and they took them away.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
